    var SCORE_TYPE = {
      WORLD: 1,
      FOLLOWING: 2,
      OTHERS: 3
    }

var LeaderboardScore = function(serializedObject) {
    this.user = null;
    this.value = -1;
    this.rank = -1;
    this.deserialize(serializedObject);
}

LeaderboardScore.prototype.deserialize = function(object) {
    if(object == null)
        return null;
           
    if(object.user != undefined) {
        this.user =  new User(JSON.parse(object.user));
    }
    this.value = object.value;
    this.rank = object.rank;
}

LeaderboardScore.prototype.getUser = function() {
    return this.user;
}

LeaderboardScore.prototype.getValue = function() {
    return this.value;
}

LeaderboardScore.prototype.getRank = function() {
    return this.rank;
}


LeaderboardScore.SCORE_TYPE = SCORE_TYPE;
module.exports = LeaderboardScore;
